name: Soul Chef Catering
address: The Astor Theatre Stanhope Road CT14 6AB
description: Jamaican takeaway based at The Astor Theatre in Deal.  ‘Grab & Go’ lunch available Wednesday to Saturday 12:30-3pm  Main menu available:   Friday and Saturday evening 5-9pm   Sunday 12:30-4pm  Check our Facebook or Instagram for lunch and dinner menu.  We deliver right to your doorstep in Deal and the surrounding areas:  Dinner only - on Fridays and Saturdays (5-8pm)  Lunch only - on Sundays (2:30-4pm)  Pre order required for delivery.  Last orders for deliveries must be placed by 4pm on Friday/Saturday for evening delivery.  Last orders for Sunday lunch deliveries must be placed by 10pm on Saturday.  No pre order required for walk-ins.
